article.headline: Providence secures 86-52 victory against Wagner
article.description: — Davonte Gaines' 21 points helped Providence defeat Wagner 86-52 on Tuesday night.
article.story: PROVIDENCE, R.I. -- — Davonte Gaines' 21 points helped Providence defeat Wagner 86-52 on Tuesday night. Gaines also contributed five assists for the Friars (6-1). Bryce Hopkins scored 20 points and added six rebounds. Josh Oduro finished 5 of 8 from the field to finish with 12 points. Melvin Council Jr. finished with 17 points, eight rebounds and two steals for the Seahawks (2-4). Zaire Williams added 12 points and two steals for Wagner. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
